description: You've reached the food storage room.  All this walking around has made you very hungry so you decide to take a few minutes and eat some food.  Yum, the food is delicious!  You need to continue on your way however.  So you put the food down after eating your fill and head out.  There are several directions you can go. You can go north, east, southwest, and west
